tan ta sharahi bigrish ni badri ( nepali : तँ त साह्रै बिग्रिस नि बद्रि , ( translation : you have been very spoiled badri ) is a 2000 nepali comedy film which tells the story about badri which has two wives but the first takes revenge on him for cheating on her .   after the success of this movie they have released sequel of this movie " taa ta sarai sprish ni badri " but this movie was n't quite successful as tan ta sarai bigris ni badri .